OL,7,FA lorry driver with an "arrogant and
OL,8,Fselfish attitude to driving" was
OL,9,Fscrolling pornography on his phone
OL,10,Fmoments before crashing into the back
OL,11,Fof a car - killing a father-of-two, a
OL,12,Fcourt has heard.
OL,14,FDanny Aitchison, 46, died when the
OL,15,F"heavily distracted" Neil Platt, 43,
OL,16,Ffailed to spot the stationary traffic
OL,17,Fon the road ahead of him while driving
OL,18,Falong the M58 at Skelmersdale, in
OL,19,FLancashire, on 17 May 2024.
