OL,5,Cdad-of-two
OL,7,FDashcam footage showed Platt looking
OL,8,Fat his phone, as photographs of naked
OL,9,Fwomen appeared on his X social media
OL,10,Ffeed.
OL,12,FThe distracted driver struck Mr
OL,13,FAithchison's Hyundai Kona car at 57mph
OL,14,Fas he waited at the end of a queue,
OL,15,Fpushing it into the rear of a tanker.
OL,17,FThe dad-of-two's car exploded into
OL,18,Fflames on impact.
