OL,5,Cdad-of-two
OL,7,FJailing Platt for 10 years, Judge Ian
OL,8,FUnsworth KC said he was a "multi-tonne
OL,9,Faccident waiting to happen".
OL,11,F"Your arrogant and selfish attitude to
OL,12,Fdriving was quite breathtaking," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"You willingly and without any excuse
OL,16,Fchose to ignore the laws of the road.
OL,18,F"This was not a one-off glance on your
OL,19,Fphone... you were looking at such
OL,20,Fthings as X, TikTok and YouTube.
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@AOUzD@AOU
