OL,7,F"The collision that occurred could
OL,8,Fhave happened anywhere along that
OL,9,Fjourney.
OL,11,F"The blunt reality is you travelled
OL,12,Fwell over 100 miles in what was
OL,13,Fsometimes a highly distracted state.
OL,15,F"In short, you were a multi-tonne
OL,16,Faccident waiting to happen."
OL,18,FPlatt, of Bootle, Merseyside, pleaded
OL,19,Fguilty at an earlier hearing to
OL,20,Fcausing the death of Mr Aitchison,
OL,21,Ffrom Liverpool.
