OL,7,FThe collision took place just before
OL,8,F1pm after police had earlier put in
OL,9,Fplace a rolling roadblock after
OL,10,Freports of a woman pedestrian on the
OL,11,Fmotorway.
OL,13,FMr Aitchison was at the end of a queue
OL,14,Fin lane one but Platt failed to notice
OL,15,Fthe stationary traffic and applied his
OL,16,Fbrakes only 35 metres away and just
OL,17,F1.5 seconds before impact.
OL,19,FDashcam footage showed Platt
OL,20,Fdistracted by his phone
