OL,7,FJudge Unsworth said there was no
OL,8,Fevidence to suggest the defendant was
OL,9,Fsearching for porn before the crash
OL,10,Fbut said he had "prioritised looking
OL,11,Fat social media" over the welfare and
OL,12,Fsafety of other road users.
OL,14,FHe told him: "You were distracted by
OL,15,Fdoing something so mindblowingly
OL,16,Fstupid.
OL,18,F"You were not paying attention to what
OL,19,Fwas ahead but you were paying
OL,20,Fattention to your phone.
