OL,7,F"It beggars belief that while in
OL,8,Fcharge of that muli-tonne vehicle you
OL,9,Fwere looking at social media and
OL,10,Fscrolling X in which some of the
OL,11,Fcontent was pornographic in nature."
OL,13,FMr Aitchison's partner Kerry, mother
OL,14,Fto his children Ella, 17, and Jack,
OL,15,F10, told the court she was on the
OL,16,Fphone to him at the time of his death
OL,17,Fand assumed his battery had run out of
OL,18,Fcharge.
OL,20,F"I feel angry he has lost his life in
OL,21,Fsuch a way.
