OL,7,F"He was just coming home to me and the
OL,8,Fkids. Their hero has gone."
OL,10,FIn a victim impact statement Ella, who
OL,11,Fwas doing her GCSEs at the time, told
OL,12,Fthe court Platt "must have known your
OL,13,Factions could have killed someone".
OL,15,F"There was a death of all things since
OL,16,Flast year, what was and what could
OL,17,Fhave been. Memories never made and
OL,18,Fplans never fulfilled," the teenager
OL,19,Fsaid.
