OL,7,F"No, you didn't mean to kill my dad
OL,8,Fand all that died alongside him, but
OL,9,Fyou must have known your actions could
OL,10,Fhave killed someone.
OL,12,F"We have lost a beacon of light in our
OL,13,Ffamily, and no matter how much I try
OL,14,Fto be like him I can't restore what
OL,15,Fshould never have been left so soon."
OL,17,FStephen McNally, defending, said
OL,18,F"family-orientated" Platt, a father
OL,19,Fhimself, was "genuinely remorseful".
