OL,7,FMr Aitchison's mother, Jeanette
OL,8,FAitchison, said: "Danny had a good
OL,9,Frelationship with every member of our
OL,10,Ffamily.
OL,12,F"He was a constant presence in their
OL,13,Flives.
OL,15,F"He was the centre of our family, he
OL,16,Fwas always there for his friends and
OL,17,Fcolleagues, Danny would do anything
OL,18,Ffor anyone.
OL,20,F"The loss of Danny has had a
OL,21,Fsignificant impact on me and my family.
